1
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:36,200
Cooling herbal tea to beat the heat!

2
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,799
Warm, nourishing ginger tea!

3
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:38,760
Come try it, come take a look!

4
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,359
You again?

5
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,599
And you're hurt again.

6
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,239
This line of work is way too dangerous.

7
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,519
If you keep this up,

8
00:01:54,519 --> 00:01:55,560
sooner or later you'll get yourself killed.

9
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,719
Cut the crap.

10
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:01,000
Hand over the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art.

11
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:04,120
Tell me where that jade pendant came from,

12
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,840
and I might consider it.

13
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:08,400
Why does everyone want that thing?

14
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,719
It's my prize.

15
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:11,319
Not for trade, not for sale.

16
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,159
And definitely not for free.

17
00:02:15,319 --> 00:02:17,039
All I know is it's tied to the Mystic Medicine Association.

18
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:22,199
Now will you hand it over?

19
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,280
Sure.

20
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,159
It's right here on me.

21
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,560
What did you do?

22
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,439
Treated your condition.

23
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,240
No need to thank me.

24
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:37,560
You...

25
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,599
Run!

26
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:18,120
That was a special case just now.

27
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,039
Sit here.

28
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:26,919
I'll massage it out for you.

29
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:35,000
Though we haven't gotten along well today,

30
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,719
I never pick and choose who I treat.

31
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:41,120
Okay.

32
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:01,680
That medicine doesn't match the symptoms.

33
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,719
The patient is dying.

34
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:04,840
If I don't change it, do I just watch him die?

35
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:07,159
This is a place for healing and saving lives.

36
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:09,319
You don't put the patient's safety first,

37
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,919
yet you're here fussing over rules?

38
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,199
Do you rank lives when saving people?

39
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,600
If you want to heal and save lives,

40
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:21,360
don't waste your talent.

41
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:23,639
Come back to Premier Pharmacy as a consultant pharmacist.

42
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:27,160
The status, money, and resources you want,

43
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:28,079
I can give them all to you.

44
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:35,680
Could she also be tied to my origins?

45
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:42,920
Those conditions you mentioned,

46
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,279
I suppose I could consider them.

47
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,759
But I have a condition too.

48
00:04:48,759 --> 00:04:49,600
Speak.

49
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:55,720
This is my first time in Qijiang too.

50
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,240
I don't know anyone or anything here.

51
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,639
I don't even have a place to stay.

52
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:05,959
That's easy.

53
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,920
I'll have Xiaoqiu arrange it in a bit.

54
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,120
The best hotel in the whole city.

55
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:16,759
I'll only feel at ease staying at your home, Ms. Ye.

56
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,399
Then I have a condition too.

57
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,399
You capitalists,

58
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,319
it's so hard to take advantage of you.

59
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:29,319
You'll represent Green Wood Hall

60
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:31,680
in the Herb Mastery Examination at the Medicine King Ceremony.

61
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,319
I thought it was something serious.

62
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,319
An exam?

63
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,120
That's my specialty.

64
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,519
Then here's to our partnership,

65
00:05:43,519 --> 00:05:44,800
may it go smoothly.

66
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:47,000
I promise not to embarrass you, Ms. Ye.

67
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:26,600
Welcome back to the hall, Young Mistress.

68
00:06:42,519 --> 00:06:46,040
Green Wood Hall doesn't just manage the Mystic Medicine Association's herb vault,

69
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,560
it also handles all herb cultivation and preparation.

70
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,600
This compound, along with the surrounding herb fields,

71
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,439
the vault, and the Ye family ancestral home,

72
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:54,519
make up the core territory.

73
00:06:57,240 --> 00:07:00,000
Green Wood Hall really is something else.

74
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:08,120
By the sound of it,

75
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:11,120
the Ye family doesn't seem to need me at all.

76
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,199
But none of this has anything to do with me.

77
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:15,000
Aren't you the young mistress?

78
00:07:27,279 --> 00:07:28,920
Air quality alert.

79
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,720
What's going on?

80
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,000
High-concentration odor detected.

81
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:44,319
Air quality alert. High-concentration odor detected.

82
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,839
Air quality alert. High-concentration odor detected.

83
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:55,720
What's that supposed to mean?

84
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,000
Is it targeting me?

85
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:01,839
Air quality alert. High-concentration odor detected.

86
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:07,680
Where did the young mistress pick him up?

87
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,199
He stinks!

88
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,040
Ye Qingxue!

89
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:17,839
Save me!

90
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,360
Ye Qingxue, help me!

91
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,519
Is she serious?

92
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,120
Help!

93
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,199
Stay back!

94
00:08:29,079 --> 00:08:29,360
You!

95
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,360
Don't come any closer!

96
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,200
Stop right there!

97
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,440
Young Mistress, Head Apothecary Ye is looking for you.

98
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:37,159
Stop!

99
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:38,720
Take him to get washed up.

100
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:40,840
Ms. Ye!

101
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,039
You can't just leave me here!

102
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,159
Where are we going?

103
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:43,559
Move.

104
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:45,159
To clean up the mess you brought.

105
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:47,639
Let me go!

106
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:52,080
Let go! I can walk on my own!

107
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,879
Ms. Ye, save me!

108
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:57,080
Ms. Ye!

109
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,519
A girl should behave herself.

110
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,799
Who gave you permission

111
00:09:21,799 --> 00:09:23,240
to bring random strays back?

112
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:26,559
Don't you forget,

113
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:28,600
you're still engaged to the Yang family.

114
00:09:29,919 --> 00:09:31,559
You have the nerve to mention the Yangs?

115
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,519
Ye Zhentian,

116
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:36,320
my affairs are none of your business.

117
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:39,679
Who I bring home

118
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:41,000
is not for you to question.

119
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,840
I'm your father.

120
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,720
From the moment you stubbornly

121
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:52,000
denied Mother the Tech Faction's treatment

122
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,000
and caused her death,

123
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:54,919
you stopped being my father.

124
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:01,519
The Mystic Medicine Association was a sanctuary for true healers.

125
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:05,559
Now it's just a chessboard for you old relics

126
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:06,919
to fight over power and influence.

127
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,360
If you can't end this conflict,

128
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,320
then I will.

129
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:15,200
You?

130
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:18,440
A merchant with mediocre medical skills?

131
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:22,159
At least I have conviction,

132
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:23,799
just like Mother.

133
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,960
Maybe I couldn't before,

134
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,559
but now I have help.

135
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:32,759
That...

136
00:10:33,759 --> 00:10:35,840
That backwoods bumpkin of unknown origin?

137
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,559
I think you

138
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:44,440
really want to destroy our Green Wood Hall.

139
00:10:47,519 --> 00:10:49,120
Yes, he comes from the countryside,

140
00:10:49,799 --> 00:10:53,720
but he's pure, honest, and capable,

141
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,879
far better than you fame-chasing hypocrites.

142
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:01,639
You go on about lineage and seniority,

143
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:04,200
long forgetting what a healer's compassion means.

144
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:07,120
I'm going to use him

145
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,960
to cut out this rotten flesh myself

146
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:13,360
and restore the Mystic Medicine Association to what it should be.

147
00:11:19,759 --> 00:11:22,399
You insolent brat!

148
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:49,519
What does the Ye family have to do with me?

149
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:55,720
A traitor has emerged in the Mystic Medicine Association.

150
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,039
Govern motion through stillness

151
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,720
Master chaos through composure

152
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,720
Your Sea-Pacifying Mind Art

153
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:18,000
rivals even your father's mastery.

154
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,919
Who on earth is he?

155
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,639
Ms. Ye.

156
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,320
Calling me out this late

157
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,600
better be for something urgent.

158
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,440
One minute.

159
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,279
Get dressed and come out.

160
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:59,320
Then leave, would you?

161
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:03,799
Relax, there's nothing on you worth seeing.

162
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,360
Who are you?

163
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:43,080
She actually took my fingerprints in secret.

164
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,120
Ms. Ye,

165
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,879
is this really necessary?

166
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,120
I treat you as one of us,

167
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,159
yet you're playing spy games with me?

168
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,720
No name,

169
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,799
no past,

170
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:57,720
no background.

171
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:01,600
Yet you beat many masters of the Mystic Medicine Association,

172
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:03,399
and won the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art.

173
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:04,399
Who exactly are you?

174
00:14:12,559 --> 00:14:14,039
Who I am isn't important.

175
00:14:16,759 --> 00:14:18,600
If you need me to,

176
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,480
I can be anyone.

177
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:23,960
Very well.

178
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:28,399
Then from today on,

179
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:31,240
you'll be the last heir of the Yang family,

180
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,080
Yang Yunfan.

181
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,120
Me?

182
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,440
The last heir of the Yang family?

183
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,960
Ms. Ye, you must be joking.

184
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,519
You've been reading too many body-double novels.

185
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,840
The Sea-Pacifying Mind Art

186
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,960
is the Yang family's hereditary cultivation art.

187
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,759
As long as you master it,

188
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:54,759
I'll handle the rest.

189
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:03,240
Back when my grandfather, Medicine Sovereign Fuguang,

190
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,519
arranged the engagement between me and Yang Yunfan,

191
00:15:06,039 --> 00:15:07,639
he had a pair of jade pendants made.

192
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:10,320
After the Yang family was wiped out,

193
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:12,039
his pendant was lost.

194
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,759
I had an identical one made.

195
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,559
It can prove your identity.

196
00:15:25,919 --> 00:15:27,559
Don't worry.

197
00:15:27,559 --> 00:15:29,639
Hardly anyone has seen Yang Yunfan.

198
00:15:29,639 --> 00:15:33,559
Besides, I control half of the Mystic Medicine Association's profits.

199
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,039
Whoever I say you are,

200
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,679
that's who you are.

201
00:15:41,639 --> 00:15:45,759
Aren't you afraid I have ulterior motives?

202
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,279
My rule is: never use those you doubt,

203
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:50,039
and never doubt those you use.

204
00:15:50,039 --> 00:15:51,639
Of course, you can refuse.

205
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,320
However,

206
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,960
if others find out

207
00:15:55,960 --> 00:15:57,320
that you're Number Zero,

208
00:15:57,919 --> 00:16:00,240
your life won't be easy either.

209
00:16:03,919 --> 00:16:05,240
So from now on, should I call you

210
00:16:07,039 --> 00:16:08,720
my fiancée?

211
00:16:12,159 --> 00:16:13,240
Don't flatter yourself.

212
00:16:13,759 --> 00:16:15,720
Only by mastering the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art

213
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,519
can you truly be called the young master of the Yang family.

214
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:21,919
Don't worry.

215
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,720
I'll make a triumphant return,

216
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:27,120
and become the Dragon King's son-in-law.

217
00:16:47,039 --> 00:16:49,279
Could I really be Yang Yunfan?

218
00:17:13,799 --> 00:17:16,319
Isn't this the very art I used before?

219
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:20,079
Could I really be Yang Yunfan?

220
00:17:23,519 --> 00:17:24,319
Who's there?

221
00:17:25,160 --> 00:17:26,440
The young lady sent me to bring you clothes.

222
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,880
Well, she's got some conscience after all.

223
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,839
You again? Seriously?

224
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:44,559
Hand over the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art.

225
00:17:44,559 --> 00:17:45,359
And I'll spare your life.
